<item>
            <title>[LUDOC-75] Add lst utility environment variable: LST_FEATURES</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LUDOC-75</link>
                <project id="10070" key="LUDOC">Lustre Documentation</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;In ticket &lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-521&quot; title=&quot;lnet-selftest add_test failure&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-521&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;LU-521&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;, a new lst utility environment variable, LST_FEATURES, was added as a way to indicate what features to enable for the lst session.  This ticket has been created to update the documentation regarding this variable.  &lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Basically, a value of &quot;1&quot; for LST_FEATURES turns on Variable Page Size for testing.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
